survey_response.review_text: I have visited Jas Dental for  re-root canal treatment, it was done by a specialist, Dr Tausif took care of time to time dressing of the tooth,  he is well behaved Doctor, you can ask all your questions to him without hesitation, his reply is always prompt, overall I had a good experience with him.

Doctor patiently listened to my concerns & based on his checkup he did detailed cleanup very gently ,later adviced me for further care at home. Also he has prescribed me a gel.
The equipment in clinic  is very much latest I felt. Anyone can surely visit this clinic for dental problems.

Visited to show the pain having in the already filled tooth, Doctor went step by step to find out the root cause of the problem and informed root canal has to be done , which convinced me to go ahead with this treatment . overall I can say good treatment is done.

It was my first experience with this clinic and it was really good. Dr. madhu explained the things very clearly. Dr.treated my problem very well, and the main part was JAS DENTAL staff called on my cell twice n asked "how I am feeling Now". It was really very good, moreover u feel special with this sort of treatment.
The doctor explained everything in detail. Thank you for yet another........... wonderful experience................

I visited clinic 1st November 2015. Behavior of staff was very good. Doctor very well explained about the procedure of treatment and also anatomy. Treatment procedure was scientific with modern equipments. Definitely recommend others.
My son was feeling comfortable while removing his milk teeth.the doctor understood his concern and removed the teeth without much pain.we were happy to visit next time.
I suffered a lot of pain cos of my impacted wisdom tooth,then doctor easily removed my wisdom tooth. Jas dental staff was so kind and helpful, I would like to visit again. Thanks....
